            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulus</ex></expan> Postumius <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>uli</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epos</ex></expan> Albinus duovir lege <lb n="2"/>Plaetoria reficiundam coeravit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Es handelt sich möglicherweise um A. Postumius Albinus Luscus, cos. 180 v.Chr., censor 174 v.Chr.</p>
